  "detailed_description": "I created a catalogue of 5 artists, by guiding the player through a virtual art gallery. During the experience each work of art is enhanced in some way, but without altering its identity. The experience is about 5 minutes long and is best experienced seated or standing with the audio turned up!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n*************WHEN YOU RUN IT PRESS THE SPACE BAR TO CALIBRATE YOUR POSITION*************<br />\r\n<br />\r\n****To close press ALT+F4****<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe artists:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1. Rachel Ara<br />\r\n2. Jacek Ludwig Scarso<br />\r\n3. Ian Chamberlin<br />\r\n4. Nemo Nonnenmacher<br />\r\n5. Scarlet Mueller<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLet me know what you think!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCheers,<br />\r\nFelix",
  "about_the_game": "I created a catalogue of 5 artists, by guiding the player through a virtual art gallery. During the experience each work of art is enhanced in some way, but without altering its identity. The experience is about 5 minutes long and is best experienced seated or standing with the audio turned up!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n*************WHEN YOU RUN IT PRESS THE SPACE BAR TO CALIBRATE YOUR POSITION*************<br />\r\n<br />\r\n****To close press ALT+F4****<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe artists:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1. Rachel Ara<br />\r\n2. Jacek Ludwig Scarso<br />\r\n3. Ian Chamberlin<br />\r\n4. Nemo Nonnenmacher<br />\r\n5. Scarlet Mueller<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLet me know what you think!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCheers,<br />\r\nFelix",
